  "reference_number": "RUS2126",
  "remarks": "\nYakub Salmanovich ZAKRIEV (hereafter ZAKRIEV) is an “involved person” under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following ground:  ZAKRIEV is involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by working as a director (whether executive or non-executive), trustee or other manager, or equivalent, of JSC H&N  an entity which is carrying on business in a sector of economic significance to the Government of Russia.\n",
